[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1103[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2 ->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/cmsvirt.[0m[1;92mc:1096[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1103[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1096[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Make sure we have proper formatters[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1097[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX,[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1098[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv ->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1099[0m[39m:        | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1100[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1101[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Apply the transfor to colorants.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1102[0m[39m:    for [0m[1;39m([0m[33mi[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1103[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2 ->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Overview  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   The stack-buffer-overflow arises because `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` passes a [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m-byte local buffer [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`i.i`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m as the input pixel data to `cmsDoTransform` without [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorrectly specifying that the input is a single‐channel index. Internally, [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`CachedXFORM → UnrollChunkyBytes` reads `nChan` bytes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhere `nChan` was left set [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto the number of output color channels, e.g. [0m[1;36m3[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m from this [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte buffer, [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverrunning it by at least [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m byte.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Root Cause  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` [0m[1;39m([0m[39msrc/cmsvirt.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, the call  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       `[0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX, … | [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[39mExitChannels[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     sets **only** the output format [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnumber of channels, bytes, endianness, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The **input** format remains `TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX` with no `CHANNELS_SH` [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mapplied, so the transform framework retains the previous input channel count [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moutput color space channels[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, not [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m.  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Consequently, `CachedXFORM` invokes `UnrollChunkyBytes` with `nChan = [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mExitChannels`, reading past the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte loop index buffer.[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Strategy  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. In `src/cmsvirt.c`, locate `cmsTransform2DeviceLink`, around line [0m[1;36m1096[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m1099[0m[39m. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Change the input‐format argument to include `[0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, so that the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtransform pipeline knows the input pixels are single‐channel indices.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Pseudo-diff:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Before:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform,[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX,[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m After:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform,[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,                        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m <— ensure [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-channel input[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Justification  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Correctness**: Explicitly setting `[0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` ensures [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`CachedXFORM`[0m[35m/[0m[39m`UnrollChunkyBytes` sees `nChan == [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m` and only reads one byte from [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe local buffer, preventing overflow.  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Minimal impact**: Only the named-color devicelink path is altered; all other[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcolor transformation logic remains unchanged.  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Performance**: No extra heap allocations or runtime checks; purely a [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mformat-flag adjustment.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Preserves existing tests**: The behavior for all other transform consumers [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis untouched; existing test suites remain valid.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Side Effects & Mitigation  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Risk**: If any legacy code assumed more channels on the “index” path, that [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpath would now correctly see only one input channel. No known dependent code uses [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmulti‐channel named‐color indices.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Mitigation**: Run regression tests, including the named-color devicelink [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzzer and existing profile conversion tests, to confirm functional equivalence.[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Verification  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Rebuild `lcms` against AddressSanitizer and confirm that [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer` no longer triggers the stack‐buffer‐overflow.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run full regression suite to ensure no unintended breakage.  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Optionally, add a targeted unit test: create a named-color transform for a [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprofile with >[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m color channels and verify no memory errors under ASan.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. References  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Similar flag usage: other calls to `cmsChangeBuffersFormat` always specify [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mboth `TYPE_*` and `[0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` for the input side. Adopt the same pattern here.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Core logic in `CachedXFORM` and `UnrollChunkyBytes` expects accurate channel [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcounts for both input and output buffers.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>src/cmsvirt.[0m[1;92mc:1096[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1103[0m[39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m[12/29/25 09:31:44][0m[2;36m [0m[34mINFO    [0m Prism Supervisor Routing: TeamStatus.EVALUATE -> TeamStatus.ANALYZE                  ]8;id=882629;file:///home/user/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py\[2m__init__.py[0m]8;;\[2m:[0m]8;id=763666;file:///home/user/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py#160\[2m160[0m]8;;\

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m20[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m LIABLE FOR ANY CLAIM, DAMAGES OR OTHER LIABILITY, WHETHER IN AN ACTION[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m21[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m OF CONTRACT, TORT OR OTHERWISE, ARISING FROM, OUT OF OR IN CONNECTION[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m22[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m WITH THE SOFTWARE OR THE USE OR OTHER DEALINGS IN THE SOFTWARE.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m23[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m24[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[95m------------------------------------------------------------------------------[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [95m---[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m25[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m26[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m27[0m[39m:#include [0m[32m"lcms2_internal.h"[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m28[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m29[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m PostScript ColorRenderingDictionary and ColorSpaceArray[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m30[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m31[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m32[0m[39m:#define MAXPSCOLS   [0m[1;36m60[0m[39m      [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Columns on tables[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m33[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m34[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[39m*[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m35[0m[39m:    Implementation[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m36[0m[39m:    --------------[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m37[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m38[0m[39m:  PostScript does use XYZ as its internal PCS. But since PostScript[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m39[0m[39m:  interpolation tables are limited to [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m bits, I use Lab as a way to[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m40[0m[39m:  improve the accuracy, favoring perceptual results. So, for the creation[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m41[0m[39m:  of each CRD, CSA the profiles are converted to Lab via a device[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m42[0m[39m:  link between  profile -> Lab or Lab -> profile. The PS code necessary to[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m43[0m[39m:  convert Lab <-> XYZ is also included.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m44[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m45[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m46[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m47[0m[39m:  Color Space Arrays [0m[1;39m([0m[39mCSA[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m48[0m[39m:  [0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m==================================================================================[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m49[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m50[0m[39m:  In order to obtain precision, code chooses between three ways to implement[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m51[0m[39m:  the device -> XYZ transform. These cases identifies monochrome profiles [0m[1;39m([0m[39moften[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m52[0m[39m:  implemented as a set of curves[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, matrix-shaper and Pipeline-based.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m53[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m54[0m[39m:  Monochrome[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m55[0m[39m:  -----------[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m56[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m57[0m[39m:  This is implemented as [0m[35m/[0m[95mCIEBasedA[0m[39m CSA. The prelinearization curve is[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m58[0m[39m:  placed into [0m[35m/[0m[95mDecodeA[0m[39m section, and matrix equals to D50. Since here is[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m59[0m[39m:  no interpolation tables, I do the conversion directly to XYZ[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m60[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m61[0m[39m:  NOTE: CLUT-based monochrome profiles are NOT supported. So, [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcmsFLAGS_MATRIXIN[0m[1;33mPUT[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m62[0m[39m:  flag is forced on such profiles.[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m63[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m64[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m[[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[95mCIEBasedA[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m65[0m[39m:      <<[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m66[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[95mDecodeA[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m transfer function [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m bind[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m67[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[95mMatrixA[0m[39m [0m[1;39m[[0m[39mD50[0m[1;39m][0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m68[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[95mRangeLMN[0m[39m [0m[1;39m[[0m[39m [0m[1;36m0.0[0m[39m cmsD50X [0m[1;36m0.0[0m[39m cmsD50Y [0m[1;36m0.0[0m[39m cmsD50Z [0m[1;39m][0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m69[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[95mWhitePoint[0m[39m [0m[1;39m[[0m[39mD50[0m[1;39m][0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m70[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[95mBlackPoint[0m[39m [0m[1;39m[[0m[39mBP[0m[1;39m][0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m71[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[95mRenderingIntent[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mintent[0m[1;39m)[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m72[0m[39m:      >>[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m73[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m][0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m74[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m75[0m[39m:   On simpler profiles, the PCS is already XYZ, so no conversion is required.[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m76[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m77[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m78[0m[39m:   Matrix-shaper based[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m79[0m[39m:   -------------------[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m80[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m81[0m[39m:   This is implemented both with [0m[35m/[0m[95mCIEBasedABC[0m[39m or [0m[35m/[0m[95mCIEBasedDEF[0m[39m depending on the[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m82[0m[39m:   profile implementation. Since here there are no interpolation tables, I do[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m83[0m[39m:   the conversion directly to XYZ[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m84[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m85[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m86[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m87[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m[[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[95mCIEBasedABC[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m88[0m[39m:            <<[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m89[0m[39m:                [0m[35m/[0m[95mDecodeABC[0m[39m [0m[1;39m[[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39mtransfer1[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39mtransfer2[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39mtransfer3[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m [0m[1;39m][0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m90[0m[39m:                [0m[35m/[0m[95mMatrixABC[0m[39m [0m[1;39m[[0m[39mMatrix[0m[1;39m][0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m91[0m[39m:                [0m[35m/[0m[95mRangeLMN[0m[39m [0m[1;39m[[0m[39m [0m[1;36m0.0[0m[39m cmsD50X [0m[1;36m0.0[0m[39m cmsD50Y [0m[1;36m0.0[0m[39m cmsD50Z [0m[1;39m][0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m92[0m[39m:                [0m[35m/[0m[95mDecodeLMN[0m[39m [0m[1;39m[[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m dup dup [0m[1;39m][0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m93[0m[39m:                [0m[35m/[0m[95mWhitePoint[0m[39m [0m[1;39m[[0m[39mD50[0m[1;39m][0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m94[0m[39m:                [0m[35m/[0m[95mBlackPoint[0m[39m [0m[1;39m[[0m[39mBP[0m[1;39m][0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m95[0m[39m:                [0m[35m/[0m[95mRenderingIntent[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mintent[0m[1;39m)[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m96[0m[39m:            >>[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m97[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m][0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m98[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m99[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m100[0m[39m:    CLUT based[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m101[0m[39m:    ----------[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m102[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m103[0m[39m:     Lab is used in such cases.[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m104[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m105[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m[[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[95mCIEBasedDEF[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m106[0m[39m:            <<[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m107[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[95mDecodeDEF[0m[39m [0m[1;39m[[0m[39m <prelinearization> [0m[1;39m][0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m108[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[95mTable[0m[39m [0m[1;39m[[0m[39m p p p [0m[1;39m[[0m[39m<[0m[33m...[0m[39m>[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m][0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m109[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[95mRangeABC[0m[39m [0m[1;39m[[0m[39m [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m][0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m110[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[95mDecodeABC[0m[1;39m[[0m[39m <postlinearization> [0m[1;39m][0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m111[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[95mRangeLMN[0m[39m [0m[1;39m[[0m[39m [0m[1;36m-0.236[0m[39m [0m[1;36m1.254[0m[39m [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m[1;36m-0.635[0m[39m [0m[1;36m1.640[0m[39m [0m[1;39m][0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m112[0m[39m:               % [0m[1;36m-128[0m[39m/[0m[1;36m500[0m[39m [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m+[0m[1;36m127[0m[39m/[0m[1;36m500[0m[39m [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m  [0m[1;36m-127[0m[39m/[0m[1;36m200[0m[39m [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m+[0m[1;36m128[0m[39m/[0m[1;36m200[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m113[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[95mMatrixABC[0m[39m [0m[1;39m[[0m[39m [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m][0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m114[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[95mWhitePoint[0m[39m [0m[1;39m[[0m[39mD50[0m[1;39m][0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m115[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[95mBlackPoint[0m[39m [0m[1;39m[[0m[39mBP[0m[1;39m][0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m116[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[95mRenderingIntent[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mintent[0m[1;39m)[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m117[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m][0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m118[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m119[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m120[0m[39m:  Color Rendering Dictionaries [0m[1;39m([0m[39mCRD[0m[1;39m)[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m121[0m[39m:  ==================================[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m122[0m[39m:  These are always implemented as CLUT, and always are using Lab. Since CRD are[0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m154[0m[39m:    return accum;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/cmsxform.[0m[1;92mc:201[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m207[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m201[0m[39m:    stride.BytesPerLineIn = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;  [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Not used[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m202[0m[39m:    stride.BytesPerLineOut = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m203[0m[39m:    stride.BytesPerPlaneIn = Size * [0m[1;35mPixelSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp->InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m204[0m[39m:    stride.BytesPerPlaneOut = Size * [0m[1;35mPixelSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp->OutputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m205[0m[39m:           [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m206[0m[39m:    p -> [0m[1;35mxform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp, InputBuffer, OutputBuffer, Size, [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m, &stride[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m207[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The ASan failure originates in UnrollChunkyBytes consuming more input bytes [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthan the stride allocated, based on a misconfigured InputFormat channel count.  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `cmsTransform2DeviceLink`, we set the transform’s InputFormat to [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX` without specifying the number of input channels [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`CHANNELS_SH`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and extra alpha [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`EXTRA_SH`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m flags. As a result, [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mPixelSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` yields an undersized stride [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`BytesPerPlaneIn`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, leading [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mUnrollChunkyBytes to read past the buffer.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The attempted patch [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m only adds a [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msingle input channel, but fails to include the mandatory extra channel [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfor the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindex[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and/or properly reflect the number of real input channels expected by the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnamed-color pipeline.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Strategy to Compute Correct InputFormat  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Identify the actual number of input components for named-color transforms.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Named-color profile links expect each pixel to consist of:  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        • One gray/intensity or index channel [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[39m component[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, plus  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        • If a named-color profile contains a colorant, an alpha or ‘extra’ [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomponent might be used [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdepending on Extra flags[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Review CreateNamedColorDevicelink: it loops over named colors, calling [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, so it feeds a single [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m16[0m[39m-bit index [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`&i`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m as input – thus exactly one [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit input channel, no extra [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbytes.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Derive correct InputFormat flags:  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Input type: TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Bytes per component: [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bits[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, so `[0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Number of channels: exactly [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m, so `[0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - No extra alpha channel: `[0m[1;35mEXTRA_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdefault[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - No swapping or premultiplication: default bits [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Adjust `cmsChangeBuffersFormat` call to explicitly include `[0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand `[0m[1;35mEXTRA_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mif needed[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, ensuring that `[0m[1;35mPixelSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m = Channels * [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBytesPerComponent + Extra = [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m*[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m = [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m`. This yields `BytesPerPlaneIn = Size*[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m = [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m`, matching exactly the single [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit index value.  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Implementation Steps  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. In `cmsvirt.c` inside `cmsTransform2DeviceLink`, replace the existing [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsChangeBuffersFormat` invocation with an explicit InputFormat combining all [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrelevant flags:  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - [0m[1;39m([0m[39mOptional[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m `[0m[1;35mEXTRA_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` if the macro system requires explicit zeroing of [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mExtra bits.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Keep the OutputFormat unchanged, as it did not trigger the overflow.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Validate that `cmsChangeBuffersFormat` correctly parses these flags to set [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`p->InputFormat` and, through the stride computation in `cmsDoTransform`, [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`BytesPerPlaneIn = [0m[1;35mPixelSize[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m = [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m` as expected.  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Rebuild and rerun the fuzzer to verify that UnrollChunkyBytes no longer [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverruns its `wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m` buffer.  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Example Patch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpseudocode[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Before:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform,[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX,[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m After:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Input: single [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit named-color index; Output: as before[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform,[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[39m*| [0m[1;35mEXTRA_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m if [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mneeded *[0m[35m/[0m[39m,[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Justification  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By explicitly specifying `[0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and `[0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in the [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInputFormat, `cmsDoTransform`’s stride calculation becomes accurate [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`BytesPerPlaneIn = [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - UnrollChunkyBytes will now process exactly [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m input channel of [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes without [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverrunning its internal `wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m` array.  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This change preserves the existing named-color device-link logic and output [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mformat; no harness or external code is modified.  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - There are no side effects on other transform pathways, as only the named-color[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindex transform format is altered. Other color transforms use separate calls to [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsChangeBuffersFormat`.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This approach matches other codebase examples where input formats for [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msingle-channel transforms are configured [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., grayscale pipelines[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m using `TYPE_* [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m| [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Verification  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Reproduce the fuzzer run under ASan with the patched binary; expect no [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack-buffer-overflow in UnrollChunkyBytes.  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run the full LCMS regression test suite to ensure no unintended breakages in [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mother color transformations.  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Confirm that named-color device links still produce correct colorants for [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mknown profiles.  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to the named‐color index formatter call. After applying the patch, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe same overflow remains at the same call stack location, indicating the root [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcause was not addressed.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Initial Issue[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Failure mode**: A [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte read overflow on the stack [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`stack-buffer-overflow`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min `UnrollChunkyBytes` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Trigger**: Running `cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer` with a malformed or specially [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcrafted input via libFuzzer.[0m                                                        [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. UnrollChunkyBytes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130[0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Frame details**: In `cmsTransform2DeviceLink`, a local variable [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`i.i`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moccupies bytes [0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m32[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m36[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and an access at offset [0m[1;36m36[0m[39m overruns this object.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Observations from the Initial Log[0m                                               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The overflow stems from unpacking or packing routines [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`UnrollChunkyBytes`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m that [0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m72[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
