[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m74[0m[39m:#define ANYSPACE        [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m31[0m[1;39m)[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m75[0m[39m:#define ANYCHANNELS     [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m15[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m76[0m[39m:#define ANYEXTRA        [0m[1;35mEXTRA_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m7[0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m77[0m[39m:#define ANYPLANAR       [0m[1;35mPLANAR_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m78[0m[39m:#define ANYENDIAN       [0m[1;35mENDIAN16_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m79[0m[39m:#define ANYSWAP         [0m[1;35mDOSWAP_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m80[0m[39m:#define ANYSWAPFIRST    [0m[1;35mSWAPFIRST_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m81[0m[39m:#define ANYFLAVOR       [0m[1;35mFLAVOR_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m82[0m[39m:#define ANYPREMUL       [0m[1;35mPREMUL_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m83[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m84[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m85[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Suppress waning about info never being used[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m86[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m87[0m[39m:#ifdef _MSC_VER[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m88[0m[39m:#pragma [0m[1;35mwarning[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdisable : [0m[1;36m4100[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m89[0m[39m:#endif[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m90[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m91[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Unpacking routines [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bits[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-----[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m92[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m93[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m94[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Does almost everything but is slow[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m95[0m[39m:static[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m96:c[0m[39mmsUInt8Number* [0m[1;35mUnrollChunkyBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCMSREGISTER _cmsTRANSFORM* info,[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m97[0m[39m:                                  CMSREGISTER cmsUInt16Number wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m,[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m98[0m[39m:                                  CMSREGISTER cmsUInt8Number* accum,[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m99[0m[39m:                                  CMSREGISTER cmsUInt32Number Stride[0m[1;39m)[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m100[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The ASan report shows a [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte read past the end of a [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte stack slot [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`i.i`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in `cmsTransform2DeviceLink`. Investigation reveals that the code passes [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`&i` [0m[1;39m([0m[39ma [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m-bit variable[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m as the source pixel buffer into a transform whose “input” [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mformatter still uses the generic [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m-bit unpacker `UnrollChunkyBytes`. That packer [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munconditionally reads `nChan` bytes plus any “extra” padding from the source [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer, overrunning the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte `i` slot.[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The previous patch tried to force the input formatter to [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, but:[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • It did not change which unpacker is selected [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe code still picked [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`UnrollChunkyBytes`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `cmsChangeBuffersFormat` silently ignored the extra flags for the [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnamed-color path.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     Hence the transform still used [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m-bit logic and mis‐sized the read.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Strategy to Fix[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. In `CreateNamedColorDevicelink` [0m[35m/[0m[39m `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsvirt.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Do not shove raw `&i` into a pipeline that expects pixel data via the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchunky-bytes packer.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Instead, create a small [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m-byte buffer on the stack, store the named-color [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindex as a [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit value in native or big-endian order, and pass that buffer to [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsDoTransform`. That buffer will be at least [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes long and satisfy [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`UnrollChunky16` or `UnrollChunkyBytes` safely.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Force the input packer to the [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit unpacker [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`UnrollChunky16`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, by [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msetting `TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX` plus `[0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in the *output* [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39msource[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m formatter, so the transform machinery picks the correct unpacker.[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         - Call `[0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform,  TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX,  [0m[35m/[0m[39m* input [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mfeed[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m*[0m[35m/[0m[39m  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                         [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; [0m[35m/[0m[39m* source [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mformat *[0m[35m/[0m[39m  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           Or use the API [0m[1;39m([0m[39mif available[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m that sets input/output formats separately:[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mcmsSetInputFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX|[0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Allocate a stack buffer `cmsUInt16Number src[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m][0m[39m; src[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mi;` then:[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, src, nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. This guarantees that `UnrollChunky16` will be selected [0m[1;39m([0m[39mits code reads [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexactly [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes, no over-reads[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and buffer length matches.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. Verify Pack/Unpack Logic[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Confirm in `cmsChangeBuffersFormat` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsio.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m or `BuildTransform` that [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` selects `UnrollChunky16`, not `UnrollChunkyBytes`.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Add an explicit assertion or branch in the named-color pipeline builder: if[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, then set the [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit packer function pointer instead of the [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m-bit [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mone.[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Steps to Implement[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. In `cmsvirt.c`, around line [0m[1;36m1094[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m1210[0m[39m:[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Remove the existing loop that does:[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         for [0m[1;39m([0m[33mi[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, [0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Instead, write:[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         cmsUInt16Number srcIndex;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform,[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        &srcIndex,            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m input fmt now [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant,[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Actually assign before each call:[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         srcIndex = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mi;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39m…[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Right after creating `xform`, before the loop, explicitly configure the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msource formatter:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mcmsSetInputFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39m xform,[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;39m([0m[39mOr if only `cmsChangeBuffersFormat` is available, call it with the 2nd [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39margument as above, and 3rd argument as the exit color format.[0m[1;39m)[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Ensure that the local buffer is large enough [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and that we never read[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmore than [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Preservation of Logic[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We keep the same named-color pipeline, colorant count, and overall transform [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcalls.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We only change how the index is fed in: from a raw integer to a tiny [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m-byte [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer, matching the intended [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit input format.[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No harness, test, or utility routines are modified; only the source file [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsvirt.c` is touched.[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Side Effects and Mitigation[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This change does not affect other pipelines: it only applies when building a [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnamed-color devicelink.[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We explicitly set the input format for named color indices to [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit, which is[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe documented internal representation.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A short regression run on existing test suites ensures no behavior changes in [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munrelated paths.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Verification[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Rebuild with AddressSanitizer and rerun `cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer`; confirm [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat the ASan overflow in `UnrollChunkyBytes` is gone.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add a small fuzz input that triggers named‐color transforms in CI to catch [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mregressions early. [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1m([0mn evals: [1;36m4[0m, patch status: PatchStatus.UNCOMPILABLE[1m)[0m                                 [2m               [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m309[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m310[0m[39m:                [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m No gamut check at all[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m311[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mcmsPipelineEvalFloat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfIn, fOut, p->Lut[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m312[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m313[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m314[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m315[0m[39m:            output = p->[0m[1;35mToOutputFloat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp, fOut, output, [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mStride->BytesPerPlaneOut[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m316[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m317[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m318[0m[39m:        strideIn += Stride->BytesPerLineIn;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m319[0m[39m:        strideOut += Stride->BytesPerLineOut;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m320[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m321[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m322[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m323[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m324[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m325[0m[39m:static[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m326[0m[39m:void [0m[1;35mNullFloatXFORM[0m[1;39m([0m[39m_cmsTRANSFORM* p,[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m327[0m[39m:                    const void* in,[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m328[0m[39m:                    void* out, [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m329[0m[39m:                    cmsUInt32Number PixelsPerLine,[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m330[0m[39m:                    cmsUInt32Number LineCount,[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m331[0m[39m:                    const cmsStride* Stride[0m[1;39m)[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m332[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m333[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m334[0m[39m:    cmsUInt8Number* accum;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m335[0m[39m:    cmsUInt8Number* output;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m336[0m[39m:    cmsFloat32Number fIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mcmsMAXCHANNELS[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m337[0m[39m:    size_t i, j, strideIn, strideOut;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m338[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m339[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35m_cmsHandleExtraChannels[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp, in, out, PixelsPerLine, LineCount, Stride[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m340[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m341[0m[39m:    strideIn = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m342[0m[39m:    strideOut = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m343[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mmemset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfIn, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfIn[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m344[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m345[0m[39m:    for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < LineCount; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m346[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m347[0m[39m:           accum = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt8Number*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in + strideIn;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m348[0m[39m:           output = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt8Number*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m out + strideOut;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m349[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m350[0m[39m:           for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mj = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; j < PixelsPerLine; j++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minclude/lcms2_plugin.h:[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m200[0m                                                        [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m269[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Floating point forward interpolation. Full precision interpolation using [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfloats. This is not a[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m270[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m time critical function. Implementation may be tetrahedral or trilinear, and [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mplug-ins may[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m271[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m choose to implement any other interpolation algorithm.[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m272[0m[39m:typedef void [0m[1;39m([0m[39m* _cmsInterpFnFloat[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsFloat32Number const Input[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m,[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m273[0m[39m:                                   cmsFloat32Number Output[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m,[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m274[0m[39m:                                   const struct _cms_interp_struc* p[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m275[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m276[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m277[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m278[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m This type holds a pointer to an interpolator that can be either [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bits or [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfloat[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m279[0m[39m:typedef union [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m280[0m[39m:    _cmsInterpFn16       Lerp16;            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Forward interpolation in [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bits[0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m285[0m[39m:#define CMS_LERP_FLAGS_16BITS             [0m[1;36m0x0000[0m[39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m The default[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m286[0m[39m:#define CMS_LERP_FLAGS_FLOAT              [0m[1;36m0x0001[0m[39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Requires different [0m  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/cmsxform.[0m[1;92mc:350[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m400[0m                                                              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m360[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m361[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bit precision [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m------------------------[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m362[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m363[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Null transformation, only applies formatters. No cache[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m364[0m[39m:static[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m365[0m[39m:void [0m[1;35mNullXFORM[0m[1;39m([0m[39m_cmsTRANSFORM* p,[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m366[0m[39m:               const void* in,[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m367[0m[39m:               void* out,[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m368[0m[39m:               cmsUInt32Number PixelsPerLine,[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m369[0m[39m:               cmsUInt32Number LineCount,[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m370[0m[39m:               const cmsStride* Stride[0m[1;39m)[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m371[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m372[0m[39m:    cmsUInt8Number* accum;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m373[0m[39m:    cmsUInt8Number* output;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m374[0m[39m:    cmsUInt16Number wIn[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mcmsMAXCHANNELS[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m375[0m[39m:    size_t i, j, strideIn, strideOut;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m376[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m377[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35m_cmsHandleExtraChannels[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp, in, out, PixelsPerLine, LineCount, Stride[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m378[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m379[0m[39m:    strideIn = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m380[0m[39m:    strideOut = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m381[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mmemset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mwIn, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mwIn[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m382[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m383[0m[39m:    for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < LineCount; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m384[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m385[0m[39m:        accum = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt8Number*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39min + strideIn;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m386[0m[39m:        output = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt8Number*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mout + strideOut;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m387[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m388[0m[39m:        for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mj = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; j < PixelsPerLine; j++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m389[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m390[0m[39m:            accum = p->[0m[1;35mFromInput[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp, wIn, accum, Stride->BytesPerPlaneIn[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m391[0m[39m:            output = p->[0m[1;35mToOutput[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp, wIn, output, Stride->BytesPerPlaneOut[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m392[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m393[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m394[0m[39m:        strideIn += Stride->BytesPerLineIn;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m395[0m[39m:        strideOut += Stride->BytesPerLineOut;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m396[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m397[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m398[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m399[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m400[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Overview  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   The root cause of the ASan crash is that `CreateNamedColorDevicelink` calls  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     `[0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX, …[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   without specifying byte-width or channel count. As a result, downstream code [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`UnrollChunkyBytes`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m interprets the input buffer with incorrect `nChan` and [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Bytes` fields, overrunning the small stack slot holding the loop index `i`. The [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfix is to supply a complete format mask combining [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX|[0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and to pass a [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit index [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvariable to `cmsDoTransform`.[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Files to patch  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - src/cmsvirt.c[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch steps  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. In `CreateNamedColorDevicelink`, locate the call to `cmsChangeBuffersFormat`.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mReplace:  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX,  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      with:  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform,  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX   [0m[35m/[0m[39m* named-color index type *[0m[35m/[0m[39m  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m             [0m[35m/[0m[39m* [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m-byte width *[0m[35m/[0m[39m  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,          [0m[35m/[0m[39m* one channel [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe index[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m[39m  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Just before the transformation loop, declare a [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit source index:  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        cmsUInt16Number srcIndex;  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      Replace the old loop, which passed `&i`, by:  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            srcIndex = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m i;  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &srcIndex, nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Crucially, do not introduce or remove any unmatched braces. Ensure the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Error:` label and cleanup remain inside the same function scope.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Justification  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ensures the internal `InputFormat` bits [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[33mT_BYTES[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m`, `[0m[33mT_CHANNELS[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m match a single [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit index channel.  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `UnrollChunkyBytes` will now set `[0m[33mnChan[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m` and read exactly two bytes per [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39melement, eliminating out-of-bounds reads.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Using a dedicated [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit `srcIndex` aligns the actual data size with the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeclared format.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This preserves all existing logic in `CreateNamedColorDevicelink`, including [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39merror handling and cleanup, and does not alter any harness, test, or external [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibrary code.[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Potential side effects and mitigation  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Named-color devicelink transforms now use an explicit format. Behavior for [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorrect input will be unchanged; only incorrect or malformed input will no longer [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtrigger a buffer overflow.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No other paths in the codebase rely on `TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX` alone, so [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthere is no regression risk elsewhere.  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - After the patch, re-run the fuzzer and test suite to confirm the issue is [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mresolved and no new warnings or errors arise.[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Example patched snippet [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfor context only[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```c[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Ensure named-color index is treated as a single [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit channel[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform,[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Transform each named color index using a [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit local variable[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        cmsUInt16Number srcIndex;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            srcIndex = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m i;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &srcIndex,[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                           nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAn AddressSanitizer stack-buffer-overflow was discovered when fuzzing the [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cms_virtual_profile_fuzzer`. The overflow occurs during a read in [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`UnrollChunkyBytes` called from `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` in `src/cmsvirt.c`. A [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatch was applied that modifies the buffer format setup [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`cmsChangeBuffersFormat`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand replaces the loop index passed to `cmsDoTransform` with a local [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsUInt16Number srcIndex`. After rebuilding and rerunning the fuzzer, the same [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack-buffer-overflow recurred at a slightly shifted stack offset in the same [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunction.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fuzzer invocation triggered an AddressSanitizer error: [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m“stack-buffer-overflow on address … READ of size [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m” inside `UnrollChunkyBytes` [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`src/lcms/src/cmspack.[0m[1;92mc:130:13[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The overflow originates from `cmsTransform2DeviceLink` [0m[1;39m([0m[39min [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`src/lcms/src/cmsvirt.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, where a local stack buffer is overrun by one byte.  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - ASan reports the overflow offset relative to the stack frame and names the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maffected objects [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`i.i`, `dwFlags.addr`, `FrmIn`, `FrmOut`, `LUT`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Key Observations in the Initial Log  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The crash stack trace:  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. `UnrollChunkyBytes`  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. `CachedXFORM`  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. `cmsDoTransform`  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. `CreateNamedColorDevicelink`  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. `cmsTransform2DeviceLink`  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - ASan shadow bytes show a partial redzone at offset [0m[1;36m36[0m[39m of the stack frame.  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The overflow occurs when reading from an input LUT or intermediate buffer [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39massembled on the stack.[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `src/cmsvirt.c`, inside `cmsTransform2DeviceLink`, the call to [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsChangeBuffersFormat` was expanded to include explicit byte and channel shifts: [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```diff[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX,[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     + [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform,[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     +     TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The loop applying `cmsDoTransform` was changed to use a `cmsUInt16Number [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrcIndex` instead of the plain `int i`:  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```diff[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     -     [0m[1;35mcmsDoTransform[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform, &i, nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant, [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     + cmsUInt16Number srcIndex;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < nColors; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m29[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m This module handles all formats supported by lcms. There are two flavors, [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbits and[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m30[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m floating point. Floating point is supported only in a subset, those formats [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mholding[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m31[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m cmsFloat32Number [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes per component[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and double [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmarked as [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m bytes per [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomponent[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m32[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m as special case[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m33[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m34[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m ---------------------------------------------------------------------------[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m35[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m37[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m This macro return words stored as big endian[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m38[0m[39m:#define [0m[1;35mCHANGE_ENDIAN[0m[1;39m([0m[39mw[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m    [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m41[0m[39m:#define [0m[1;35mREVERSE_FLAVOR_8[0m[1;39m([0m[39mx[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m     [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt8Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0xff[0m[39m-[0m[1;39m([0m[39mx[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m42[0m[39m:#define [0m[1;35mREVERSE_FLAVOR_16[0m[1;39m([0m[39mx[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m    [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0xffff[0m[39m-[0m[1;39m([0m[39mx[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m43[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m44[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m0xffff[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m0xff00[0m[39m = [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m255[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m257[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m255[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m256[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m = [0m[1;36m257[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m256[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m45:c[0m[39mmsINLINE cmsUInt16Number [0m[1;35mFomLabV2ToLabV4[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number x[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
