[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m576[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mmemset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mwIn, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mwIn[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m577[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mmemset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mwOut, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mwOut[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m578[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m579[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Get copy of zero cache[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m580[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39m&Cache, &p->Cache, [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCache[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m581[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m582[0m[39m:    strideIn = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m583[0m[39m:    strideOut = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m584[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m585[0m[39m:    for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < LineCount; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m586[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m587[0m[39m:        accum = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt8Number*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39min + strideIn;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m588[0m[39m:        output = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt8Number*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mout + strideOut;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m589[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m590[0m[39m:        for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mj = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; j < PixelsPerLine; j++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m591[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m592[0m[39m:            accum = p->[0m[1;35mFromInput[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp, wIn, accum, Stride->BytesPerPlaneIn[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m593[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m594[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mmemcmp[0m[1;39m([0m[39mwIn, Cache.CacheIn, [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCache.CacheIn[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m595[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m596[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mwOut, Cache.CacheOut, [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCache.CacheOut[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m597[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m598[0m[39m:            else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m599[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mTransformOnePixelWithGamutCheck[0m[1;39m([0m[39mp, wIn, wOut[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m600[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/lcms2_internal.h:[0m[1;36m180[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m260[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m180[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m181[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Fast floor restricted to [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m..[0m[1;36m65535.0[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m182:c[0m[39mmsINLINE cmsUInt16Number [0m[1;35m_cmsQuickFloorWord[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsFloat64Number d[0m[1;39m)[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m183[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m184[0m[39m:    return [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsUInt16Number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;35m_cmsQuickFloor[0m[1;39m([0m[39md - [0m[1;36m32767.0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + 32767U;[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m185[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m186[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m187[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Floor to word, taking care of saturation[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m188:c[0m[39mmsINLINE cmsUInt16Number [0m[1;35m_cmsQuickSaturateWord[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmsFloat64Number d[0m[1;39m)[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m189[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m190[0m[39m:    d += [0m[1;36m0.5[0m[39m;[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m191[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39md <= [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m192[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39md >= [0m[1;36m65535.0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0xffff[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m193[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m194[0m[39m:    return [0m[1;35m_cmsQuickFloorWord[0m[1;39m([0m[39md[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m195[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m196[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m197[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Test bed entry [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpoints---------------------------------------------------------------[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m198[0m[39m:#define CMSCHECKPOINT CMSAPI[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m199[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m200[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Pthread support [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m--------------------------------------------------------------------[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m201[0m[39m:#ifndef CMS_NO_PTHREADS[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m202[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m203[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m This is the threading support. Unfortunately, it has to be [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mplatform-dependent because [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m204[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m windows does not support pthreads. [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m205[0m[39m:#ifdef CMS_IS_WINDOWS_[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m206[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m207[0m[39m:#define WIN32_LEAN_AND_MEAN [0m[1;36m1[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m208[0m[39m:#include <windows.h>[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m209[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m210[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m211[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m The locking scheme in LCMS requires a single [0m[32m'top level'[0m[39m mutex[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m212[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m to work. This is actually implemented on Windows as a[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m213[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m CriticalSection, because they are lighter weight. With[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m214[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m pthreads, this is statically inited. Unfortunately, windows[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m215[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m can't officially statically init critical sections.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m216[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m217[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m We can work around this in [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m ways.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m218[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m219[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m We can use a proper mutex purely to protect the init[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m220[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m of the CriticalSection. This in turns requires us to protect[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m221[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m the Mutex creation, which we can do using the snappily[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m222[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m named InterlockedCompareExchangePointer API [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpresent on[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m223[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m windows XP and above[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m224[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m225[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m In cases where we want to work on pre-Windows XP, we[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m226[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m can use an even more horrible hack described below.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m227[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m228[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m So why wouldn't we always use [0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m? Because not calling[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m229[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m the init function for a critical section means it fails[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m230[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m testing with ApplicationVerifier [0m[1;39m([0m[39mand presumably similar[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m231[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m tools[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m232[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m233[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m We therefore default to [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m, and people who want to be able[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m234[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m to run on pre-Windows XP boxes can build with:[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m235[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m     CMS_RELY_ON_WINDOWS_STATIC_MUTEX_INIT[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m236[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m defined. This is automatically set for builds using[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m237[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m versions of MSVC that don't have this API available.[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m238[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m239[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m From: [0m[4;94mhttp://locklessinc.com/articles/pthreads_on_windows/[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m240[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m The pthreads API has an initialization macro that has no correspondence to [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39manything in [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m241[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m the windows API. By investigating the internal definition of the critical [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msection type, [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m242[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m one may work out how to initialize one without calling [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mInitializeCriticalSection[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m243[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m The trick here is that [0m[1;35mInitializeCriticalSection[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is not allowed to fail. [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIt tries [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m244[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m to allocate a critical section debug object, but if no memory is available, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mit sets [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m245[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m the pointer to a specific value. [0m[1;39m([0m[39mOne would expect that value to be NULL, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbut it is [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m246[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m actually [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvoid *[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m for some reason.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Thus we can use this special value for[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat [0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m247[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m pointer, and the critical section code will work.[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m248[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m249[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m The other important part of the critical section type to initialize is the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnumber [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m250[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m of waiters. This controls whether or not the mutex is locked. Fortunately, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthis [0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m251[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m part of the critical section is unlikely to change. Apparently, many [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprograms [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m252[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m already test critical sections to see if they are locked using this value, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mso [0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m253[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Microsoft felt that it was necessary to keep it set at [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m for an unlocked [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcritical[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m254[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m section, even when they changed the underlying algorithm to be more [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mscalable. [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m255[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m The final parts of the critical section object are unimportant, and can be [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mset [0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m256[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m to zero for their defaults. This yields to an initialization macro:[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m257[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m258[0m[39m:typedef CRITICAL_SECTION _cmsMutex;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m259[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m260[0m[39m:#ifdef _MSC_VER[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1235[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!hProfile[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m goto Error;                    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m can't allocate[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1236[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1237[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mcmsSetProfileVersion[0m[1;39m([0m[39mhProfile, Version[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1238[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1239[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mFixColorSpaces[0m[1;39m([0m[39mhProfile, xform -> EntryColorSpace, xform -> [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mExitColorSpace, dwFlags[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1240[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1241[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Optimize the LUT and precalculate a devicelink[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1242[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1243[0m[39m:    ChansIn  = [0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform -> EntryColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1244[0m[39m:    ChansOut = [0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform -> ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1245[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1246[0m[39m:    ColorSpaceBitsIn  = [0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform -> EntryColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1247[0m[39m:    ColorSpaceBitsOut = [0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform -> ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1248[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/cmspack.[0m[1;92mc:100[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m115[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m100[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m101[0m[39m:    cmsUInt32Number nChan      = [0m[1;35mT_CHANNELS[0m[1;39m([0m[39minfo -> InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m102[0m[39m:    cmsUInt32Number DoSwap     = [0m[1;35mT_DOSWAP[0m[1;39m([0m[39minfo ->InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m103[0m[39m:    cmsUInt32Number Reverse    = [0m[1;35mT_FLAVOR[0m[1;39m([0m[39minfo ->InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m104[0m[39m:    cmsUInt32Number SwapFirst  = [0m[1;35mT_SWAPFIRST[0m[1;39m([0m[39minfo -> InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m105[0m[39m:    cmsUInt32Number Extra      = [0m[1;35mT_EXTRA[0m[1;39m([0m[39minfo -> InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m106[0m[39m:    cmsUInt32Number Premul     = [0m[1;35mT_PREMUL[0m[1;39m([0m[39minfo->InputFormat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m107[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m108[0m[39m:    cmsUInt32Number ExtraFirst = DoSwap ^ SwapFirst;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m109[0m[39m:    cmsUInt32Number v;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m110[0m[39m:    cmsUInt32Number i;  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m111[0m[39m:    cmsUInt32Number alpha_factor = [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m112[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m113[0m[39m:    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mExtraFirst[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m114[0m[39m:        [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m115[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mPremul && Extra[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   After the first patch, the overflow shifted but did not go away because [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mUnrollChunkyBytes was still using the *old* InputFormat flags:   [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - It was mis-interpreting the named‐color index buffer as an [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m-bit “chunky” [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mformat [0m[1;39m([0m[39mUnrollChunkyBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m instead of a [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit format.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - It inherited extra/swap/flavor/premul fields from the original transform, so [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnChan or Extra was >[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor non-zero[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, causing UnrollChunkyBytes to read past the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msingle‐index buffer on the stack [0m[1;39m([0m[39meither the original `i` or `srcIndex`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Critical Logic to Preserve  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We must continue to drive the named-color index transform one index at a time [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrough `cmsDoTransform` and write into `nc2->List[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.DeviceColorant`.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We cannot change the loop structure or drop `cmsDoTransform`.  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We must continue to use the existing pipeline machinery [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`cmsChangeBuffersFormat`, Unroll*[0m[35m/[0m[95mPack[0m[39m* routines, `CachedXFORM`, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Strategy for a Correct Patch  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. Fully override *all* InputFormat flags so that:  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - We select the correct “[0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit chunky” unroll routine [0m[1;39m([0m[39mUnrollChunkyWords[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnot UnrollChunkyBytes.  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - We explicitly set `nChan = [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39malways one index channel[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - We explicitly set `BytesPerChannel = [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit index[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - We clear any inherited Extra, DOSWAP, FLAVOR, SWAPFIRST, PREMUL bits.  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. Leave the OutputFormat as before [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfloating-point Lab or integer Lab[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m so that [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdownstream logic is unaffected.  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   C. Reapply this format override *immediately* before the per-index loop in [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`CreateNamedColorDevicelink`, so that every call to `cmsDoTransform` sees the new [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInputFormat.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Implementation Steps  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m In `src/cmsvirt.c`, inside `CreateNamedColorDevicelink`, replace the existing[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`cmsChangeBuffersFormat` call with one that:  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Passes an `inFmt` bit-pattern equal to:  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m         [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit samples[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m      [0m[1;39m([0m[39mone channel[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        | [0m[1;35mEXTRA_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m         [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno extra alpha[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        | [0m[1;35mDOSWAP_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m        [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno byte-swap[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        | [0m[1;35mSWAPFIRST_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m     [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno planar swap[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        | [0m[1;35mFLAVOR_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m        [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno reverse flavor[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        | [0m[1;35mPREMUL_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m        [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno premultiplied alpha[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Keeps the `outFmt` exactly as before:  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Remove the temporary `srcIndex` patch, since once the indexing buffer is [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtruly [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit and single‐channeled, an `int` would also work safely—but better to [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mkeep `cmsUInt16Number srcIndex` for API consistency.  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m3[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Build and rerun the fuzzer. The ASan error should no longer occur because:  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - `cmsDoTransform` will dispatch to the [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit unroller [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`UnrollChunkyWords`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, which expects exactly [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes per channel, [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m channel [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtotal—matching our buffer.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - No stray Extra or swap logic will misalign the pointer, so no out-of-bounds[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreads.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Justification  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By fully specifying *both* bytes and channels and clearing all other [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInputFormat bits, we guarantee that the unroll function and stride arithmetic line [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mup exactly with our [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m-byte per-index buffer.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We do not touch the fuzz harness, test code, or external dependencies—only one[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mline in the library.  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We preserve the named-color loop and output formatting so that existing [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunctionality is untouched.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This approach is analogous to how Gray-[0m[1;36m16[0m[39m and CMYK-[0m[1;36m16[0m[39m transforms explicitly [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mset [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m|[0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[39mn[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in other parts of the codebase [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., the CMYK/Gray [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdevicelink builders[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects & Mitigation  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If any existing code path accidentally runs this named-color logic with [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpremultiplied alpha or swap flags set, we will now forcibly clear those. But [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnamed-color index transforms never need premultiplied nor swapped data, so no real [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloss.  [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No other pipeline is affected; the change is local to the named-color [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdevicelink creator.  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Example Patch Snippet  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```diff[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m In src/cmsvirt.c, inside CreateNamedColorDevicelink:[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-   [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Make sure we have proper formatters[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-   [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform,[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-       TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-       [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-         | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-         | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+   [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Force a clean [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit, single-channel input formatter, clearing swap/extra [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mflags.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+   [0m[1;35mcmsChangeBuffersFormat[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxform,[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+       TYPE_NAMED_COLOR_INDEX [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+         | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+         | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+         | [0m[1;35mEXTRA_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+         | [0m[1;35mDOSWAP_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+         | [0m[1;35mSWAPFIRST_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+         | [0m[1;35mFLAVOR_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+         | [0m[1;35mPREMUL_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+       [0m[1;35mFLOAT_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+         | [0m[1;35mCOLORSPACE_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_cmsLCMScolorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+         | [0m[1;35mBYTES_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+         | [0m[1;35mCHANNELS_SH[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mcmsChannelsOfColorSpace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mv->ExitColorSpace[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Rebuild & retest with AddressSanitizer; the stack‐buffer‐overflow in [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`UnrollChunkyBytes` should be eliminated.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
